26
00:01:28,150 --> 00:01:30,600
Dad, what are you doing?

27
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,130
Excuse me.

28
00:01:32,130 --> 00:01:32,400
Oh?

29
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:35,190
