37
00:01:50,830 --> 00:01:52,670
Yes, of course.

38
00:01:52,670 --> 00:01:54,210
Oh! What a beautiful bird.

39
00:01:54,210 --> 00:01:55,460
Eh?

40
00:01:55,460 --> 00:01:56,840
Look there.

41
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,550
