46
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,440
Eh?

47
00:02:09,670 --> 00:02:12,020
This is really nice.

48
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:15,110
Thanks.

49
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:17,030
