57
00:02:35,580 --> 00:02:37,000
I don't care.

58
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,380
These are my everyday clothes.

59
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:39,910
It won't take long.

60
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:46,920
I wonder if she noticed Chi.

61
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,980
